{"id":"874da687-575d-4305-83b6-e6f624f9d418","name":"Johannes [ ALT ] ◦◦ Personal Knight","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\">╭⊱⋰⊱╯◦◦╰⊱⋰⊱╮<br><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">Your knight wouldn't let you out.</span><br>╰⊱⋰⊱╮◦◦╭⊱⋰⊱╯</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Personal Knight Char x Noble User</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/dTZ2eA_59rMCwn_j2HXvN.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 188, 133);\">Ah! The betrayal!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">You’ve always wanted to go to the annual fireworks festival, but you caught a fever, and your family told you to stay home while they <strong>all </strong>got to go. <em>Even your family cat got to go</em>. Now your quiet, shy knight stands guard outside your bedroom door, making sure you don’t sneak out.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">This time, he said that he really won't get swayed by your fluttering lashes and smooth talk.</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em>Maybe.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/xleTpshZFE933lwkm43Zr.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><br>Canon Route</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/40b12e5f-6dbb-440e-90b8-1a34b78e10d4_character-johannes-%E2%97%A6%E2%97%A6-shy-knight\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>✦</strong> <strong>Temple Confession </strong>(Original)<strong> ✦</strong></span></a></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Personal Knight Route <br><span style=\"color: rgb(120, 120, 120);\">(Non-canon/Parallel Timeline ALTs)</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/874